Description: (Fortified Castle|Manor|Residential Castle) Dwelling or former dwelling, feudal, royal or lordly.
(Lighthouse|NULL) Default value, whenever the general appearance of a building reveals nothing of its exact nature.
(Watchtower|NULL) Building that stands out in the landscape due to its tall shape.
(Armorer|Bank|Blacksmith|Butcher|Fishmonger|Hawker|Tailor) Place of business. If residence on site, add under Use.
(Chicken_House|Cowshed|Pigsty|Sheep Barn|Stable) Place for carrying out livestock farming activities only, without habitation.
(Barnhouse|Farm) Place for carrying out a cultural activity only, without habitation.
